<body>
    <%- include('../partials/nav.ejs') %>

        <div class="banner-container">
            <div class="banner">
                <img src="aboutBanner.png" alt="Slide 1">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="banner-text">
            <h1>Your Guide to Professional Growth</h1>
            <h3>The Right Guidance for the Right Career.</h3>
            <h4>"Explore! Empower! Succeed!</h4>
            <div class="ban-btn">
                <a href="contact"><button type="button" class="btn btn-success">Contact us</button></a>
                <a href="about"><button type="button" class="btn btn-success">Know More</button></a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="box-container">
            <h2>How does this benefit you?</h2>
            <div class="boxes">
                <div class="box box-1">
                    <div class="icon-box">
                        <i class="fa-brands fa-searchengin"></i>
                        <h4>Discover Your Ability & Skills</h4>
                    </div>
                    <p>Identify your strengths and find the right career path with personalized assessments and expert
                        guidance.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="box box-2">
                    <div class="icon-box">
                        <img src="goals.png" alt="">
                        <h4>Set Realistic Career Goals</h4>
                    </div>
                    <p>Define achievable career goals based on your strengths and interests. Get expert guidance to stay
                        focused and grow professionally.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="box box-3">
                    <div class="icon-box">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-graduation-cap"></i>
                        <h4>Explore Career Opportunities</h4>
                    </div>
                    <p>Discover career options that match your skills and interests, with insights into various
                        industries to help you find the right path.</p>
                    </div>

                <div class="box box-4">
                    <div class="icon-box">
                        <img src="confidence.png" alt="">
                        <h4>Boost Confidence</h4>
                    </div>
                    <p>Build confidence in your career journey by recognizing your strengths and overcoming challenges
                        with personalized support.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="box  box-5">
                    <div class="icon-box">
                        <img src="steps.png" alt="">
                        <h4>Develop Essential Skills</h4>
                    </div>
                    <p>Enhance your skills with personalized resources and recommendations, helping you stay competitive
                        and advance in your career.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="box box-6">
                    <div class="icon-box">
                        <i class="fa-brands fa-searchengin"></i>
                        <h4> Unlock Your Potential</h4>
                    </div>
                    <p>Get the right guidance, develop essential skills, and grow with confidence on your career journey!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-container" >
            <div class="text">
                <h2 >Why Career Guidance?</h2>
                <p>Career guidance plays a crucial role in helping individuals align their skills, values, and
                    aspirations with the right career path. It provides clarity, direction, and support, empowering
                    people to make informed decisions about their professional journey.</p>
                <p><i>"The future depends on what we do in the present." </i>– Mahatma Gandhi<br>Career guidance helps
                    individuals take actionable steps today to shape a successful tomorrow.</p>
                <p><i>"Your work is going to fill a large part of your life, and the only way to be truly satisfied is
                        to do what you believe is great work."</i> – Steve Jobs<br>With the right guidance, you can
                    identify and pursue a career that aligns with your passions and strengths, leading to greater
                    fulfillment.</p>
                <p>Career guidance helps individuals navigate challenges, set achievable goals, and build a professional
                    network, ultimately enhancing job satisfaction and career success.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="image">
                <img src="text-img.png" alt="img">
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="vertical-box">
            <h2 class="vertical-box-h2">Career Insights for You!</h2>
            <p class="para">Get personalized career advice and valuable insights to help you make informed decisions.
                Our platform empowers you to explore opportunities that match your skills and aspirations, guiding you
                toward a successful career.</p>

            <div class="container">
                <img src="book2.jpg" alt="Image 1">
                <div class="container-text">
                    <h3>Explore Your Potential</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Discover tailored career options with expert guidance.</li>
                        <li>Find pathways from entry-level roles to leadership positions, all aligned with your goals.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="container">
                <div class="container-text">
                    <h3>Guided Career Pathways</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Navigate through tailored career options with expert guidance.</li>
                        <li>From entry-level roles to leadership positions, find pathways that align with your goals.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <img src="book1.jpg" alt="Image 2">
            </div>

            <div class="container">
                <img src="guidance-img7.jpg" alt="Image 3">
                <div class="container-text">
                    <h3>Build the Skills You Need</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Access resources and recommendations to enhance your skills.</li>
                        <li>Stay competitive in your field with continuous learning and growth opportunities.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="std-container-outer">
            <h2>Carrer insights solutions for you!</h2>
            <div class="std-container">
                <div class="std-card">
                    <img src="book1.jpg" alt="">
                    <div class="std-card-body">
                        <h4>Class 8-10</h4>
                        <h5>Stream & Subject Selection</h5>
                        <p>Advanced assessment & personalised guidance to help you select the perfect stream and
                            subjects that align you to the right careers.</p>
                        <p><a href="#">View Details</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="std-card">
                    <img src="book2.jpg" alt="">
                    <div class="std-card-body">
                        <h4>Class 10-12</h4>
                        <h5>Career Selection & Planning</h5>
                        <p>Expert guidance & 5-dimensional assessment to help you discover your perfect career and
                            choose the right course and college. </p>
                        <p><a href="#">View Details</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="input-container">
